==历史==
{{seealso|英女皇寿辰|维多利亚日}}
马来西亚是由[[马来亚联合邦|马来亚联合邦]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]（于1965年8月9日独立）、[[砂拉越|砂拉越]]和[[北婆罗洲|北婆罗洲]]（现今[[沙巴|沙巴]]）组成的联邦国家，前身是[[英国殖民地|英国的殖民地]]。过去殖民地政府的公定假日包括订于6月第一、第二或第三个星期六的[[英女皇寿辰|英国君主官方诞辰]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=4 SSVF Malacca colour party, King's birthday parade, 1937.|url=http://www.malayanvolunteersgroup.org.uk/node/167|publisher=Malayan Volunteers Group|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231235908/http://www.malayanvolunteersgroup.org.uk/node/167|archivedate=2013年12月31日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Over The Horizon. Penang: Picturesque British Outpost.|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1350&dat=19560705&id=YrpOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=uwAEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4713,1799067|newspaper=Toledo Blade|date=1956-07-05|quote=Penang, a semi-tropical island northwest of Singapore, was celebrating Queen Elizabeth's birthday when we arrived. A local resident kindly relinquished his invitation that we might attend the 8 a.m. parade ground festivities.}}</ref> 这个日期是由[[爱德华七世|爱德华七世]]制定，因为6月英国本土的天气较佳，便于进行典礼活动。<ref>{{cite news|title=Windsor marks Queen's birthday with gun salute|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/berkshire/hi/people_and_places/history/newsid_8632000/8632810.stm|newspaper=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2010-04-20|quote=The tradition of two birthdays began with King Edward VII, born in November, who decided to celebrate a second birthday in June.|accessdate=2013-12-31|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505170307/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/berkshire/hi/people_and_places/history/newsid_8632000/8632810.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 现今，英国驻马来西亚最高专员署仍会在6月的英女王诞辰举行宴会，招待英国侨民和公众。<ref>{{cite news|author=Kee Hua Chee|title=Celebrating Queen Elizabeth’s birthday|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2011/06/14/celebrating-queen-elizabeths-birthday|newspaper=[[星报_(马来西亚)|星报]]|date=2011-06-14|accessdate=2020-06-10|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610145814/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2011/06/14/celebrating-queen-elizabeths-birthday|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

[[马来亚联合邦|马来亚联合邦]]于1957年独立后，依然保留庆祝君主诞辰的传统，制订6月的第一个星期六为-{zh:最高元首诞辰; zh-hans:国家元首诞辰; zh-hant:國家元首誕辰;}-。除了-{zh:最高元首诞辰; zh-hans:国家元首诞辰; zh-hant:國家元首誕辰;}-外，9个[[世袭|世袭]][[元首_(马来君主)|马来君主]]和4个[[wikt:appointment|委任]][[州元首|州元首]]的州份，都有各自州订的元首诞辰纪念日，没有元首的[[联邦直辖区|联邦直辖区]]则以{{tsl|en|Federal Territory Day|联邦直辖区日}}替代这个意义的节日。君主诞辰、元首诞辰和联邦直辖区日典礼的行事包括阅操、阅旗、晋谒元首、册封、授勋及宴会活动。

